          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Unlocking Capital for Small Businesses Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill (1) requires the Securities and Exchange Commission to establish registration requirements for&nbsp;private-placement brokers and finders that are no more stringent&nbsp;than those imposed on crowdfunding portals, and (2) otherwise modifies provisions related to private-placement brokers and finders.</p>]]></text>
